            <p>Founded in Feb of 2015 and based in Christchurch, New Zealand, iKitchen is a trusted community marketplace for people to list, discover, and share unique nice foods around the world — online or from a mobile phone.Whether Asian food for a dinner, hot food for a party, or just food for mouth, iKitchen connects people to unique food experiences, at any style points. iKitchen is the easiest way for people who want to sharing their extra space and food skills or just come to enjoy.</p>
